Products






































































Search













Our Products
For over half a century world-class companies have been partnering with Sevcon to develop products that enable them to deliver their electrification strategies. Sevcon products offer in-built ‘Intelligent Control’ advanced control algorithms.
We offer a range of controllers, DC/DC converters and battery charging systems covering, battery voltages from 13V to over 800V  to satisfy a wide range of on-road, off-road, marine and construction equipment.
Increasingly customers are looking to work in partnership with Sevcon to create customised products. Some require our standard products to be repackaged to better suit the vehicle installation, integrating components together to reduce space or some work with us to create a unique electrification solution to allow for class leading functionality.





