Products






































































Search













Our Products
For over half a century world-class companies have been partnering with Sevcon to develop products that enable them to deliver their electrification strategies. Sevcon products offer in-built ‘Intelligent Control’ advanced control algorithms.
We offer a range of controllers, DC/DC converters and battery charging systems covering, battery voltages from 13V to over 800V  to satisfy a wide range of on-road, off-road, marine and construction equipment.
Increasingly customers are looking to work in partnership with Sevcon to create customised products. Some require our standard products to be repackaged to better suit the vehicle installation, integrating components together to reduce space or some work with us to create a unique electrification solution to allow for class leading functionality.





Search for a product

Search








Our Products



High Voltage Controllers 

                                Sevcon's family of high voltage controllers cover the voltage ranges 120V to over 800V DC and power levels from 10kW to 300kW.
                            
View product type






Low Voltage Controllers

                                The family of low voltage controllers cover the voltage ranges from 14V to 150V DC.
With their high reliability and compact dimensions our DC motor controllers are used on both pump and traction applications in some of the worlds leading material handling vehicles.
                            
View product type






DC/DC Converters

                                Sevcon offer a comprehensive range of converters covering battery voltages from 24V to over 800V and output voltages from 12 to 48V. As power demands increase you will find products that can satisfy power needs from 300W through to 7kW.
                            
View product type






Battery Chargers

                                Through the Bassi brand, Sevcon supply a wide range of battery chargers and power management devices for both industrial, on-vehicle and automotive applications. The voltage ranges from 24 to 820V and power levels up to 250kW.
                            
View product type






Accessories

                                To support the range of motor controllers and chargers, Sevcon offers a range of electronic gauges, displays and other components.
                            
View product type






Custom Made

                                Sevcon has over half a century of experience designing innovative motor controllers used by some of the most demanding customers throughout the world.
                            
View product type







