Trusted by the world’s leading companies for electrification solutions
Sevcon has been at the forefront of electric vehicle technology for over half a century and in that time has partnered with many of the world’s leading companies to achieve their low-carbon ambitions.
Learn more about us



Scroll Down Why Sevcon?






Why Choose Sevcon? 



























Your Electrification Partner
Sevcon is at the forefront of the ongoing global transition from fossil fuels to clean energy, from internal combustion engines to hybrid and electric vehicles. We have been designing and manufacturing high-quality motor controllers and system components for a variety of hybrid and electric vehicles for over half a century. Our partners range from leading on-road vehicle manufacturers to forklift truck and electric motorcycle makers. In choosing Sevcon you can be confident you will be working with an innovative and responsive business, one with a can-do attitude and unrivalled experience in delivering high-quality electrification solutions.
